column1: #text=We began by driving past the overloaded parking lot dreading finding a parking spot .
#text=Luckily we know of a spot on the side of the grocery store that is almost always vacant .
#text=My girlfriend and I park in our normal spot and walk inside .
#text=The store is booming with people and all the lines are full .
#text=We are the type of people who do not like a lot of people so we wanted to get in and out as fast as we could .
#text=Quickly we get all the groceries marked down on the list and we head to the checkout line .
#text=We found a shorter line that was for a lesser amount of groceries .
#text=Luckily we had 2 items less than the maximum for the line , so we hopped in and quickly got checked out and on our way .
#text=I carried the groceries out to the car rather than having the employees do it because there are much less able people who need there help more than I do .
#text=Finally we headed home and used our groceries to cook dinner .
